      "FunctionSignature": "DSCore.IO.FileSystem.GetDirectoryContents@var,string,bool",
      "Replication": "Auto",
      "Description": "將傳回給定目錄中包含的檔案與目錄清單。可使用選擇性的 searchString 篩選結果。\n\nFileSystem.GetDirectoryContents (directory: var, searchString: string = \"*.*\", includeSubdirectories: bool = false): var[]..[]"
